Please note the shape of the iceberg and where it comes into contact with water.
Here you can see how it starts to spin, and the boat has swam to the other side, and there is a person standing there.
This is a medium-sized Greenland iceberg.
It protrudes out of the water at about 120 feet or 40 meters.
But this record is in real time.
(Music) And so simply, the iceberg shows us the other side of his personality.
Thank you.
