Share your knowledge of technology, and how it concerns us, and how it concerns us.
We can discuss what we love.
We can anticipate which aspects of technology may become the most useful over time and which are the most problematic.
If we all focus on an open dialogue about AI in the future, it will help create an atmosphere of shared awareness of what AI is now, what it can become, and what we must do to get the best result for us.
